latestPosts.caption:
*ಕಲಾಶೃಂಗಾರ* 🌸

I poured my heart into this shoot, draped in a beautiful @suta_bombay saree with a unique concept featuring colorful bindis. We shot it on my neighbor’s terrace, and I’m absolutely loving the final video and my look. Huge thanks to @makeupby_plavanya for the amazing makeup and @yesh1th_portraits for capturing the video so perfectly!

No studio? No worries! Crash your neighbor’s terrace, find a spot, and click away! Let’s see how awesome it turns out!
🚀 Stay tuned – result dropping in the next video! 💕

This outfit said ‘make a statement,’ and I said ‘say less ‘ 🖤

Fit deets❤️‍🔥
Skirt from @therok.force adding that luxe flair—just here for the aesthetic 🔥

Born from stardust, dipped in gold⚜️

Not just a look 🤌this is a whole *cosmic attitude.* 
Golden sculpted corset hugging like a second skin, 
Sunburst crown straight from the heavens, 
Draped like royalty, iced in chunky gold. 

**My inner goddess is showing, and she’s not subtle.** 

Concept and styling? 100% my chaotic creative brain at work. 
Shot like a freakin’ dream by the legend himself, @chidu.ln_portraits 
And can we talk about the glam? @makeupby_plavanya popped OFF with that makeup, flower band, and corset magic — literal fairycore fantasy unlocked.

#sculptedingold #divinefemininevibe #modernmythology #SareeButMakeItPower  #crownonmoodon #ServingSolarFlares

Took a cropped shirt, threw on some bling, lungi’d up. Call it fashion therapy 🤌💋

Snagged these fire charms from @nekoa.ngel ❤️‍🔥

✨ Happy Ugadi! ✨
May this Ugadi bring you all joy, prosperity, and endless new beginnings! Wishing you success, good health, and happiness in the year ahead.
